-- MOVES-Debbie Kennedy joins Royal London from Capita
-- 
-- Tue Sep 23, 2014 09:59AM EDT
-- None



Sept 23 (Reuters) - UK mutual life and pensions company Royal London [ROLGPI.UL] said it appointed Debbie Kennedy head of protection proposition design in its intermediary division, effective Sept. 29.

Kennedy will be responsible for the division's protection proposition, encompassing Bright Grey and Scottish Provident, the company's UK intermediary protection businesses. Her responsibilities will cover the key components of product, customer experience, underwriting, claims and reinsurance, Royal London said in a statement.